message.body: Good good tryna leave work and go play! Its too lovely out!
Yeah this day is not for working! What are you going to do?
Lots of shows tonight, performance art and music....solstice celebrating :) summertiiime

Omg coconut is my fave flave. Just got out! Hollaaa! :))
